    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it does show its age. The engine starts up consistently and the car handles well on the road, but you may notice some minor vibrations at highway speeds and a slight oil leak that will need monitoring. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and a small dent on the rear passenger door, while the interior upholstery shows significant wear and some staining. It is a solid choice for someone looking for a functional vehicle who doesn't mind putting in a little work to freshen up the aesthetics.",
