    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for me. It\u2019s perfect if you're looking for something that\u2019s been well-loved and is ready to hit the road immediately without any fuss. It drives like a dream and I'd love to see it go to a great new home. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This F87-generation M2 is a meticulously maintained example featuring the N55B30T0 turbocharged inline-six, renowned for its forged crankshaft and high-pressure direct injection. The powertrain is paired with a 7-speed M Double Clutch Transmission (M-DCT) and an electronically controlled Active M Differential, ensuring optimal torque vectoring. The chassis utilizes lightweight aluminum suspension components and five-link rear geometry for superior kinematic precision. Recent service includes a comprehensive cooling system audit and fluid analysis, confirming the integrity of the vanos system and turbocharger seals. A compelling choice for the purist seeking a balanced, high-performance coupe with a documented maintenance pedigree.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Good condition. Clean title. Maintenance up to date. No mechanical issues. Minor exterior wear. Inspections welcome.",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a standout example of pride in ownership, maintained to a high standard that balances daily utility with impressive preservation. The exterior finish holds a beautiful depth, showing only minor, honest signs of road use that do not detract from its overall sharp appearance. Inside, you\u2019ll find a clean, non-smoker cabin where the seats remain supportive and the surfaces are free of any significant wear or blemishes. Every electronic component and convenience feature\u2014from the climate control to the infotainment system\u2014operates flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine is clean and responsive, benefiting from a strict adherence to its service schedule. It delivers a smooth, quiet, and predictable driving experience, making it a reliable choice for its next owner. This car represents a perfect middle ground for a buyer seeking quality and longevity without the premium of a brand-new price tag.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
